{"tid":380082,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"斷水、停電、全城停擺，颱風「天鴿」過境後的澳門","createTime":"2017-08-29T23:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T01:37:34.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5af40f20dd584c97e0d925c561f99fdd0b70bcb5","tid":380082,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:44:54.000Z","msg":"一場強颱風，讓這座金碧輝煌的賭城在一夜之間變成了滿目瘡痍的死城。這一切背後，是天災，還是人禍？<br />\n<br />\n端傳媒記者 林振東 發自澳門<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/0aefd5d9605842cbbed81229f38ee42e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2F0aefd5d9605842cbbed81229f38ee42e.jpg&h=743723a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃昏，電力依然未恢復，澳門依然漆黑一片，一名女子在街道上用手機。 攝：林振東/端傳媒 <br />\n<br />\n2017年8月23日，強颱風「天鴿」吹襲華南沿岸，對澳門造成嚴重破壞。截至24日晚，颱風造成澳門至少8人死亡、244人受傷。<br />\n由於澳門八成電力依靠中國大陸輸入，珠海輸電設備的故障引致澳門出現大範圍停電。截至24日下午，澳門有約22.5萬戶已恢復正常供電，但仍有約3萬處於低窪地區的用戶仍然受停電困擾，澳門電力已加派工程團隊進行搶修。<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/6d05ff6bc3a54ebea72b6d1804be1a7d.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2F6d05ff6bc3a54ebea72b6d1804be1a7d.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=c1ee6e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n颱風「天鴿」過境後，澳門某公園遍布樹枝和垃圾。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/ef741b2d01134896bbaeab20e5eb1d2b.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2Fef741b2d01134896bbaeab20e5eb1d2b.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=48bba004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n颱風「天鴿」吹襲後，澳門居民到市面觀察損毀情況。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/323b831cf1da49fc93aff2456da747d8.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2F323b831cf1da49fc93aff2456da747d8.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=7f672467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門筷子基快達樓的停車場在「天鴿」吹襲下，有大量洪水疑湧入，有人報稱被困，當地消防局聯同海關蛙人搜救及進行排水。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/49a1f55be3604de4a2da3df0a08379f6.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2F49a1f55be3604de4a2da3df0a08379f6.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=13fd7e72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門漁人碼頭外，有車輛被沖至大海。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/bd89865b63cb4c3b90937082e4029bbf.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2Fbd89865b63cb4c3b90937082e4029bbf.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=c9149caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門晚上的電力依然未完全恢復，部分地區只有小量燈光。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/4e87c572105a41ccbad8f537311b8f0f.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2F4e87c572105a41ccbad8f537311b8f0f.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=339a0986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門下環街，晚上仍然有不少居民在排隊取水。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/3099854636a9494ba4a7341b541517f2.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2F3099854636a9494ba4a7341b541517f2.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=df3a48e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有大廈簷蓬在颱風吹襲後塌下，消防員正在清理現場。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/acd4fe6c0c9e4e88889972e7f3d36f9b.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2Facd4fe6c0c9e4e88889972e7f3d36f9b.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=eea85fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n颱風「天鴿」的洗禮下，澳門街道上滿佈堆積如山的垃圾。 攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/824977e428b343709ac5200ced72a41d.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2F824977e428b343709ac5200ced72a41d.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=c3b980a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入夜後，澳門的街道仍然漆黑，還下起雨來，市民撐著傘，靠走過的車輛的車頭燈照明，橫越街道。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/02c6856209e043cf8c6bbd5a33425c17.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2F02c6856209e043cf8c6bbd5a33425c17.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=2b1ee26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門著名賭場「萄京娛樂場」在停電的情況下沒辦法開門營業。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/08/7d3e46b1b2d3493eb3430b3ac5fee25c.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F08%2F7d3e46b1b2d3493eb3430b3ac5fee25c.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=e00cff62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門氹仔的多間賭場附近地區，交通燈因停電而暫停運作。攝：林振東/端傳媒<br />\n風災亦對澳門三個水廠造成嚴重影響，產能接近全澳一半的青洲水廠受損最嚴重，其泵房及電機設施全被淹沒，目前仍在搶修當中。至24日下午，媽閣、新口岸、荷蘭園等地區仍然停水，或有限度供水。澳門自來水公司在全澳設置6個臨時供水點；大批居民手提水桶到特定地點取水。有澳門網民指，有商家在災後坐地起價，例如2支水售150澳門元、1個外賣飯盒售100澳門元，有酒店亦以一晚9000至14000澳門元出租房間。<br />\n<br />\n截至24日下午，全澳共錄得432宗事故報告，包括32宗建築物損毀、石屎脱落及墮下物；88宗招牌廣告、簷篷、鐵片/鐵枝、窗墜落及搖搖欲墜；9宗棚架欲墜及倒塌；97宗天線及樹木倒塌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20170825-photo-Macau-After-Typhoon/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20170825-photo-Macau-After-Typhoon%2F&d=8z1brvdlsQg%2B6kaZjdJoAk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=02f04379\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20170825-photo-Macau-After-Typhoon/</a>"},{"pid":"831fab01ad17c5ef48a1f030b8d5fe9b528c4c84","tid":380082,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:48:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8839aa26da7c80a6cd2b35ae95583d1d90b68aed","tid":380082,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪你影架?<br />\n唔係就請註明轉貼</blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159d1f1fe7233365327a361a19f37a36f680f623","tid":380082,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:53:12.000Z","msg":"世界末日咁哦陰公豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fdb4e466d313f813f39953ffb85ed73c87d086","tid":380082,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:55:51.000Z","msg":"端傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6144ac81cfb871c96518c344ef055dd9e1fd0f1","tid":380082,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世界末日咁哦陰公豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭兩張相仲以為喺北韓影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ef75cefe86232c4c416d16e44b9f9ed696e5b2","tid":380082,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>世界末日咁哦陰公豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭兩張相仲以為喺北韓影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔左咁耐都好似無乜民間自發嘅補救行動，澳門人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58a365ede4880d1b8d834b4e42101ecef9e2461","tid":380082,"uid":122540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪你影架?<br />\n唔係就請註明轉貼</blockquote><br />\n冇眼睇"},{"pid":"f95500009a8368ddec3f093e5487c712d62a9e9f","tid":380082,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:12:30.000Z","msg":"怕咩吖，我有九千蚊"},{"pid":"8ccf0178aef28906d177e1bba5aed0783db2cdcf","tid":380082,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:18:25.000Z","msg":"你們還有党呀，有乜事搵解放軍啦"},{"pid":"e52f782e7991822e4341a98c5b25fd46443783ff","tid":380082,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"入面咪話端傳媒囉～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n愛玉愛澳既端傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89948ab5057dfe63d2d0278235e0ec9c71890798","tid":380082,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T01:37:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}